data.description: This Spacious Townhome Is Located In The Great Atkinson Townhomes Subdivision! This 3 Bedrooms, 3 Bathrooms Townhome Is Perfect For A Family Or A Group Of Friends. It Has Everything You Need For A Comfortable And Convenient Living Space. It Has A Fully Equipped Kitchen With All The Appliances You Need, Including A Microwave, Dishwasher, Refrigerator, And Electric Stove, Making It Easy To Cook At Home. There Is One Bedroom Downstairs And Two Bedrooms Upstairs, Including The Primary Bedroom With Its Own En Suite Bathroom, Perfect For Relaxing After A Long Day. The Master Bathroom Has Double Sinks, A Separate Tub And Shower, And A Large Walk-In Closet.  The Townhome Is About 20 Minutes To Many Local Attractions, Such As The Houston Zoo, The Museum Of Fine Arts, And The George R. Brown Convention Center. It Is Also Within Easy Reach Of Shopping, Restaurants, And Schools, 10 Minutes To Hobby Airport. Schedule Your Showing Today!
